{"tid":832784,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[爭氣啲喇淡淡] 上源收500票速超購　屯門業主擴議價","createTime":"2018-09-23T04:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T15:06:01.000Z","uid":87069,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2af45108eeb840e9c68f0c95ff5ea98a6b991d2d","tid":832784,"uid":87069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:48:12.000Z","msg":"臨近中秋佳節，新盤收票情況熱烈。萬科置業(香港)旗下屯門上源，以低二手市價一成推出231伙，累積收票逾500張，超額認購逾1.1倍。受該盤影響，同區二手市淡靜，部分業主擴大議價空間至近6%求客。 <br />\n<br />\n上源周六(9月22日)續開放示範單位予公眾參觀，現場所見，不少睇樓客於展銷廳外排隊等候睇樓，場外有大批地產代理撈客。樓盤首批價單折實平均呎價11,073元，最平呎價9,878元。首批有逾40伙的折實樓價少於500萬元，另有近20伙的呎價少於1萬元。入場單位為2B座1樓B室一房戶，實用面積343方呎，折實售價逾424.9萬元。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180923/mobile/bkn-20180923000639485-0923_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180923%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180923000639485-0923_00842_001.html&d=3MLEuntUU0VPnla4ey6UyAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4fe8a8c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180923/mobile/bkn-20180923000639485-0923_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n早兩日撚狗俠個post啲留言先話跌到6,7000蚊呎先好入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，宜家依啲山卡啦盤都狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:  發展商做票唔計，水票好多"},{"pid":"312e9c0c976d9371fc61ece3e532bc2b7ca701ee","tid":832784,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"發展商平賣唔計"},{"pid":"1bf1d479d9ee2c91fe43f1d7a0ac5c6336eb511a","tid":832784,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83fbafbb2e64a7bfa5a48800f50b7db29387a8c","tid":832784,"uid":22173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"今次班地產商比大陸佬搞串個party<br />\n真係抵撚死<br />\n哈哈哈哈哈"},{"pid":"dbcc7d2d3864d8f60a2dfd6c0523c06dde89ac53","tid":832784,"uid":43146,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"平又輸，貴又輸<br />\n連登淡淡真係臭過狗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349813ef698157c4c580b251a268df3ff90145e0","tid":832784,"uid":37599,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"開到平過一萬蚊尺都係超額得1倍，咁都有得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f09e13fa3eb43da74a6ac45f052a6c13795c3d7","tid":832784,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"349813ef698157c4c580b251a268df3ff90145e0","tid":832784,"uid":37599,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"開到平過一萬蚊尺都係超額得1倍，咁都有得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:32:09.000Z","msg":"我估因為上車客唔會揸車返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f8d2be5926f2d008cffc3179b487776a4ee382","tid":832784,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"果盤係小欖，交通好一般"}]}